          <h2 style="color: #d9534f;">Hi {{name}},</h2>
          <p>We know how difficult it can be to revisit certain chapters of your
            life—especially the years when things went off track. But this is
            the best chance to reduce egregious penalties, and your
            participation isn’t optional—it’s mandatory.</p>
          <p>We can’t tell your story without your input. And we can’t prove to
            the IRS that you qualify for abatement—which, in some cases, can
            remove up to half of what you owe—unless you help us make the case.</p>
          <p>We’ve worked hard to get you to this point. We’ve cleared the way.
            But this last step has to come from you.</p>
          <p>Failing to respond is, effectively, turning down the relief we’ve
            been fighting to get on your behalf.</p>
          <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-weight: bold;">Call us now at
            <a
              href="tel:{{number}}"
              style="color: #d9534f; text-decoration: none;"
            >{{number}}</a>
            and let’s finish this, together.</p>
